steps.description:
The fix refactors the Notify and Listen components from the old format to the new format, properly handling Data input types:
```python
def build_notify(self) -> Data:
    data = None
    if self.data:
        if not isinstance(self.data, Data):
            if isinstance(self.data, str):
                data = Data(text=self.data)
            elif isinstance(self.data, dict):
                data = Data(data=self.data)
            else:
                data = Data(text=str(self.data))
        else:
            data = self.data
    else:
        data = Data(text="")

    if data:
        if self.append:
            self.append_state(self.name, data)
        else:
            self.update_state(self.name, data)
    else:
        self.status = "No record provided."
    self.status = data
    return data
```

